    fj.Monoid.doubleAdditionMonoid
    Since 4.7. Due to rounding errors, addition of doubles does not comply with monoid laws
    fj.Semigroup.doubleAdditionSemigroup
    Since 4.7. Due to rounding errors, addition of doubles does not comply with monoid laws
